  [USER_A] Server auth using Negotiate with user 'userA'
  [USER_A] Authorization: Negotiate S1JCNV91c2VyQTpIVFRQ...

[RESULT A] HTTP 200
[RESULT A] Body: {"identity": "KRB5_userA", "mechanism": "negotiate_complete"}

[STEP 2] User A's connection is now in the pool
[STEP 3] User B: CURLAUTH_ANY with DIFFERENT creds

  [USER_B] [POC-TRACE] url_match_result: attaching conn #1
           (result param=0, IGNORED). negotiate_state=0
